{"title":"Well","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":31,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-2592","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>给出n个正整数X1,X2,...Xn，可以进行不超过m次操作，每次操作选择一个非零的Xi，并将它减一。<br>最终要求存在某个k满足Xk=0，并且z=max{|Xi - Xi+1|}最小。<br>输出最小的z和此时最小的k。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行两个正整数n, m (1&lt;=n&lt;=1,000,000, 1&lt;=m&lt;=10^18)。第二行n个正整数X1,X2,...Xn (Xi&lt;=10^9)。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出k和z。数据保证方案一定存在。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>16 15<br>8 7 6 5 5 5 5 5 6 6 7 8 9 7 5 5</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1 2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>将X序列变为<br>0 2 4 5 5 5 5 5 6 6 7 8 9 7 5 5<br>此时k=1，z=2，共操作了8+5+2=15次。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}